  <?dbhtml filename="lxqt-desktop.html" ?>

  <title>LXQt Desktop</title>

  <para>
    LXQt is an extremely fast-performing and energy-saving desktop environment.
  </para>

  <para>
    <application>LXQt</application> is a <application>Qt</application> based
Desktop Environment. It is focused on being a classic desktop with a modern
look and feel. It can customize appearance everywhere.  The panel(s) have
plugins and settings.  It is Window Manager agnostic, has multi-language
support and standard keyboard shortcuts.  <application>LXQt</application>
uses less CPU and less RAM than most other environments. It is especially
useful for cloud computers with low hardware specifications, such as
netbooks, mobile devices (e.g. MIDs) or older computers, but can be used
with modern hardware.
  </para>

